  <num>32-1453.02</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Notice.</heading>
  <text>An employer shall post a notice in its workplace notifying employees of their rights under <cite path="32|14A">this chapter</cite>. The notice shall be posted in a conspicuous place in at least one location where employees congregate.</text>
